      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/man-la-yahduruhu-al-faqih:1:12:15",
      "source_url": "https://thaqalayn.net/hadith/34/1/12/122",
      "text": [
        " «إِذَا خَافَ اَلصُّبْحَ فَلاَ بَأْسَ بِهِ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.122 - Ali ibn Ja'far asked his brother Imam Musa ibn Jafar Al-Kadhim (as) bout a man who uses his hand to clean his teeth when he gets up for the night prayer (Salat Al Layl), even though he has access to siwak.\nImam (as) said: \"If he fears that dawn is approaching, there is no harm in doing so.\""
        ]
      }
    },
